text: Gulfran Támara (born 2 February 1996) is a Colombian footballer who plays as a central defender for Bolivian club Destroyer's. ==External links== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian footballers Category:Categoría Primera A players Category:Barranquilla F.C. footballers Category:Atlético Junior footballers Category:Association football central defenders Category:Footballers from Barranquilla
